      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-cou2-sqa-criteria",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2024 R1) is validated under an ISO 9001:2015-certified quality management system. Software version control, regression test suite (>1200 benchmark cases), change-control records, and release notes are archived in the project QMS repository. User-defined functions (UDFs) implementing the power-law hemolysis model are subject to independent code review, unit testing, and integration testing against published analytical solutions. All test records traceable to project document MCSQA-2025-001."
