      "achievedLevel": 5,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-cou2-code-verification-criteria",
      "rationale": "Numerical code verification performed using the Method of Manufactured Solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations and the scalar hemolysis transport equation. Observed order of accuracy (OOA) for velocity: 1.98 (theoretical: 2.0); for pressure: 1.95; for hemolysis scalar: 1.97. All OOA values within 2% of theoretical second-order convergence rate. Verification report MCNV-2025-003 archived with mesh sequences and MMS source term derivations."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
