      "rationale": "Three independent test articles manufactured from the same production batch, inspected by CMM to confirm geometric conformance (all critical dimensions within ±0.05 mm). Porcine whole blood sourced from a single donor pool per test session; haematocrit 35 ± 2%, MCV 62 ± 3 fL, initial plasma-free haemoglobin < 5 mg/dL confirmed by spectrophotometry. Three replicate experiments per operating point per article (n = 45 total experiments). Inter-article and intra-session variability quantified; pooled experimental uncertainty on NIH: ±3.2% (95% CI). Sample characterisation report MCTS-2025-009 archived."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
